title: Mealligram - Diet App

creator: Kilo Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Mealligram is the new go-to app to help you keep track of your daily meals and fitness with just the help of your camera!

Research has found that 78% of people who consistently keep track their meals succeeded in losing weight, so we've made it easy to log all your meals with the help of our suite of fitness tools. Just take a picture of what you're eating, log it on Mealligram, and start achieving your weight-loss goals today!

1. Keep track of your progress
- App will automatically record your meal times based on your pictures.
- Record your exercise and body changes easily by connecting the app to your Health data.
- If you forgot to take a picture, you can use emojis to record you meal.

2. Assess your diet habits and observe your changes
- Keep up with your diet at your own pace.
- Check your meal time and meal score in your calendar to assess your diet habits.
- Your meals, body condition, exercise logs... all at one place! You can also check your progress using graphs.

3. Stay healthy with people who share the same goal
- If it's hard to do it alone, start with people who have the same goal as you.
- Share your records with your groups in real-time and motivate each other.
- Finish the survival challenge and get a gift.

We are updating the features you need as quickly as possible.
If you want to give us feedback, please contact us at
support@mealligram.com

Please leave us a review if you enjoy using Mealligram!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
A new feature ‘Group’ was released.
Through this new feature, users can stay motivated by tracking their meals, exercises, and fitness levels together with friends, family and anyone with the same goals!
